**Exploring Dart telemetry issues**

I'm noticing that Dart exists, but it seems telemetry isn't allowed to write to the home directory because of sandbox rules. It looks like workspace-write prevents writing outside the workspace, trying to write to /.dart-tool. To work around this, I can disable analytics by setting the environment variable `DART_DISABLE_ANALYTICS=1` to possibly avoid the file write issue. There's also a command `dart --disable-analytics` that I can use. Let’s set the environment variable!
